query:
SELECT 
  po.id, 
  po.orderNumber, 
  po.customerOrderNumber,
  po.customerName,
  po.tenantId,
  t.name as tenantName
FROM pickingOrders po
LEFT JOIN tenants t ON po.tenantId = t.id
WHERE po.status IN ('picked', 'staged')
LIMIT 5;
